OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Health and Science
OL,8,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,10,FWith 2024 on track to be the hottest
OL,11,Fyear ever, this week countries around
OL,12,Fthe world will gather for COP29 in
OL,13,FAzerbaijan.
OL,15,FOne of the main topics of discussion
OL,16,Fwill be climate finance - how much-
OL,17,Fdeveloped nations owe developing
OL,18,Fcountries to help them adapt to the
OL,19,Feffects of global warming.
