OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FUnder the 2015 Paris Agreement, rich
OL,8,Fcountries are bound to provide finance
OL,9,Fto developing countries to help them
OL,10,Fcut emissions and cope with the
OL,11,Feffects of climate change.
OL,13,FThe current goal is to provide $100
OL,14,Fbillion (#77 billion) a year although
OL,15,Fit is widely agreed that this is not
OL,16,Fenough.
