OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FOne of the countries in need of this
OL,8,Fsupport is Zambia. It is suffering its
OL,9,Fworst drought in 40 years and 50% of
OL,10,Fthis year's crops have been lost.
OL,12,F"We are at the frontlines of receiving
OL,13,Fthe adverse impacts of climate
OL,14,Fchange," says Gabriel Pollen, the
OL,15,Fnational coordinator for the country's
OL,16,Fdisaster management and mitigation
OL,17,Funit.
