OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,F"We need to transition from merely
OL,8,Ftalking to dealing with the actual
OL,9,Frealities on the ground ` supporting
OL,10,Fdeveloping countries to build
OL,11,Fresilience in the face of climate
OL,12,Fchange."
OL,14,FZambia produces as many emissions in a
OL,15,Fyear as the UK does in ten days, and
OL,16,Fthe US produces in just 15 hours.
OL,18,FIt is also a leader in green energy `
OL,19,Fit provides 83% of its power through
OL,20,Fhydropower. Its biggest dam at Lake
OL,21,FKariba was completed in 1960.
