OL,7,FBut the drought means the reservoir
OL,8,Fand the river systems which feed it
OL,9,Fare drying up.
OL,11,FThe lake is currently running at just
OL,12,Fover 4% of its full capacity. Water
OL,13,Flevels have dropped to their lowest
OL,14,Fever from 13 metres to just 90cm.
OL,16,FCephas Museba, the senior power
OL,17,Fstation manager at the dam, says if
OL,18,Fthey continued to run power at
OL,19,Fcapacity they would run out of water
OL,20,Fin 30 days.
