OL,7,FInstead, they are having to ration
OL,8,Fwhat they put through.
OL,10,FJust one generator out of six is
OL,11,Frunning. The result is rolling power
OL,12,Foutages for Zambians. When we visited
OL,13,Fin early October, people were
OL,14,Freceiving just three hours of power a
OL,15,Fday ` usually in the middle of the
OL,16,Fnight.
