OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,F"Climate change is real because the
OL,8,Feffect for us - we are already
OL,9,Fexperiencing it... The frequency of
OL,10,Fload shedding or drought will increase
OL,11,Fand for that we need to look for
OL,12,Fanother alternative source of power,"
OL,13,Fsays Museba.
OL,15,FIn the busy capital of Lusaka, the
OL,16,Feffects of the power outages are
OL,17,Fobvious. Those with private solar
OL,18,Fpanels or diesel generators power
OL,19,Ftheir homes and businesses at extra
OL,20,Fcost.
