OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FAt Yellow Shop Barbershop, the owner
OL,8,FJulian Miti has had to cut his hours
OL,9,Fas he can only work during the
OL,10,Fdaylight.
OL,12,FHe has invested in rechargeable
OL,13,Fshavers but can no longer use other
OL,14,Ftools like his plug-in hairdryer. His
OL,15,Ftakings are down 85%.
OL,17,FJust down the road, Karen Bowa runs a
OL,18,Fbutcher's shop.
