OL,7,FShe usually has two freezers full of
OL,8,Fmeat but without power, she has had to
OL,9,Freduce the amount of meat she buys and
OL,10,Fstore it in just one of the freezers
OL,11,Fusing big ice blocks to keep it cold.
OL,13,FShe says the cost of ice has increased
OL,14,Fdramatically in the last few months `
OL,15,Falmost quadrupling as demand for it
OL,16,Frises.
