OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FThe effects can also be seen starkly
OL,8,Foutside the big cities. Commercial
OL,9,Ffarmers who rely on power for their
OL,10,Fpump irrigation are having to plant
OL,11,Ffewer crops further increasing the
OL,12,Ffood crisis.
OL,14,FAt local health posts, vaccines are
OL,15,Falso being stored on ice and delivered
OL,16,Ffrom bigger cities to keep them cold.
OL,18,FAt Chipapa Primary School in Chilanga,
OL,19,Fthey noticed female students were
OL,20,Foften staying home from school when
OL,21,Fthey were on their periods.
