OL,7,FThe charity World Vision helped build
OL,8,Fa toilet block where the girls could
OL,9,Fwash and the school saw attendance
OL,10,Fincrease. But the block is now closed
OL,11,Fas without power, water cannot be
OL,12,Fpumped in.
OL,14,FWorld Vision spokesperson Agatha Mali
OL,15,Fsays it is frustrating to see the
OL,16,Fimpact of power outages impacting
OL,17,Fpeople's lives and livelihoods.
