OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,F"Business gets slow, activities go
OL,8,Fdown, most shops are closed - most
OL,9,Fcompanies rely on power, so even if
OL,10,Fthey have generators or alternative
OL,11,Fpower sources, it's not enough to
OL,12,Fsustain them or enable them to do
OL,13,Ftheir work accordingly," she says.
OL,15,F"It would be good if we could make use
OL,16,Fof solar systems that could power our
OL,17,Fhouses, communities and work systems.
OL,18,FOf course, we'd still need some money
OL,19,Fto pay for that."
