OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FWhile the charity sector is doing its
OL,8,Fbest to help the country's neediest to
OL,9,Ftackle the impacts of the drought, the
OL,10,Fgovernment is calling for support from
OL,11,Fother nations to build its climate
OL,12,Fresilience.
OL,14,FIt argues that it needs funding to
OL,15,Fhelp promote investment in the overall
OL,16,Finfrastructure needed to cope with new
OL,17,Fextremes of weather, such as
OL,18,Fdiversifying the sources of
OL,19,Felectricity supply.
