OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,F"We are receiving support to address
OL,8,Fthe impact of climate change but it's
OL,9,Ftailored towards immediate food
OL,10,Fassistance. Nothing is being given for
OL,11,Fresilience building in order for
OL,12,Fcountries like Zambia to better
OL,13,Fwithstand the adverse impacts of
OL,14,Fclimate change" says Gabriel Pollen.
OL,16,FAs leaders gather in Baku this week to
OL,17,Fdiscuss the climate fund, countries
OL,18,Flike Zambia ` already bearing the
OL,19,Fbrunt of the crisis ` will be watching
OL,20,Fcarefully.
